    "uen": "202501874M",
    "description": "<p>Yo-Chi - Australia’s beloved frozen Yogurt &amp; Açaí Bar is now in Singapore!</p>\n<p><br>\nFounded in Melbourne, Yo-Chi is known for its fresh, guilt-free treats and vibrant in-store experience. Guests can create their own combinations from a wide range of premium frozen yogurt flavours, fruit, signature and seasonal toppings, granolas and sauces designed to be as healthy or indulgent as they like. It’s a brand that celebrates wellness, freedom of choice and community connection. At the end of day, it’s all about our guests and to create what makes them happy.</p>\n<p><br>\nAt Yo-Chi, we are on a mission to create positive energy and happiness. Our venues are vibrant<br>\nspaces for friends, family and teammates alike, united by creativity, inclusivity and fun. We are fueled by the passion and energy of our team - our true heart and soul.</p>\n<p><br>\nAs we prepare to launch Yo-Chi in Singapore, we are looking for passionate individuals to be part of<br>\nthe pioneer team! If you have got the energy and team spirit, you are gonna be just the right fit for us!</p>",
